          "body": "New term request for \"anatomical region\" as a child of   
  `EFO_0000635` (organism part).\n\n## Changes\n\n- **New term `EFO_0920090`**
  added to `efo-edit.owl`:\n  - Label: `anatomical region`\n  - Definition: *A
  region of the whole organism without well-defined compartmental boundaries. 
  *\n  - Parent: `EFO_0000635` (organism part)\n  - Cross-reference:          
  `BSPO:0000070` (equivalent term in the Biological Spatial Ontology, which is
  not directly imported by EFO)\n  - Definition PMIDs: `PMID:25140222` (BSPO  
  paper), `PMID:22293552` (UBERON paper)\n\n```xml\n\u003cowl:Class           
  rdf:about=\"http://www.ebi.ac.uk/efo/EFO_0920090\"\u003e\n                  
  \u003crdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource=\"http://www.ebi.ac.                     
  uk/efo/EFO_0000635\"/\u003e\n    \u003cobo:IAO_0000115\u003eA region of the 
  whole organism without well-defined compartmental boundaries.               
  \u003c/obo:IAO_0000115\u003e\n                                              
  \u003coboInOwl:hasDbXref\u003eBSPO:0000070\u003c/oboInOwl:hasDbXref\u003e\n 
  \u003crdfs:label xml:lang=\"en\"\u003eanatomical                            
  region\u003c/rdfs:label\u003e\n\u003c/owl:Class\u003e\n```\n\n\u0026gt;     
  [!WARNING]\n\u0026gt;\n\u0026gt;",                                          
